1. bundle install
2. comment 3rd line in users_controller.rb
3. setup your recaptcha keys in config/initializers/recaptcha.rb and configure your database in config/mongoid.yml
4. (re)start your server
5. go to yourboard.org/users and create user with 'adm' role
6. uncomment 3rd line in users_controller.rb
7. go to yourboard.org/log_in and log in as administrator
8. create categories and boards here: yourboard.org/boards
9. ?????
10. PROFIT!
